snippet.title: Karak Azgaraz | Free Update Trailer - Warhammer: Vermintide 2
snippet.description:
Karak Azgaraz is a free new content update for Warhammer: Vermintide 2. It contains three newly remastered adventure maps from the fan-favorite DLC of the first Vermintide game.

Read more about the content update:
► https://bit.ly/3OMxrGa
